{"tid":1425983,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【集中發放正能量】一人一個發夢窩心事同多謝你想多謝既手足","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T00:15:52.000Z","uid":147696,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db5bde870b3c258f8ee2806b06079d0618c83b0d","tid":1425983,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:01:41.000Z","msg":"連盈有好鬼多CDrom,近日又多左班中年銀髮既巴絲，好多都可能未去過現場，想係到俾大家睇下同知道發夢果陣既一d開心野，一齊渡過呢個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">Amazing Summer </span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我講下自己親身發夢經歷<br />\n1: 有一晚(728)同手足佢地係cwb茶記食飯，果掛就慶涷撚水，我地都驚驚地嫁，點知由坐位到飯餸都高質到不行，碗飯係大過平時足足有50%，食食下有個中年男人走過黎拎走張單話呢張單我埋，叫我地小心d，生命要緊。有手足感動到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2: 每次示威現場都有好多大係咁捐物資，有大拎住成箱水周圍走，有人拎住口罩，McDonald 包，飯盒周圍派，我前日都拎過一次包食因為已經9個鍾未食野，多謝呢位手足<br />\n<br />\n3: 728，84好彩有義載，如果唔係真係驚走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我同意義載嫁，因為可以避左好多cam,兩次義載都有衫有水俾我地飲同換(當然我自己都有準備而冇拎啦)<br />\n<br />\n4: 琴前日我係街派黑口罩支持醫護，俾幾個街坊又小又拍片，但當佢地鬧完我地(仲有個女同事一齊)後望去後面，係成十幾個街坊圍住我地安慰我地(女同事果下即喊)<br />\n<br />\n5: 至少4個人前日塞錢俾我，全部拒絕哂，但一袋袋寶礦力擺完就走，係咪想拎死我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n6: 前日我係沙田一個人做FA, 有手足俾左支ventolin我，但我話我已經有，你俾有需要既人或自己keep住，佢死都要塞俾我，結果我轉讓俾其他前線手足<br />\n<br />\n7: 73旺角再遊行，我入左team FS,有段時間我去救人同佢地失散左，我走返同佢地幾個匯合時先知好多人沖返入去搵我，其實好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地其實真係好攰呀，日日都係咁攰，日日有義士被捕，負面情緒到極點，其實<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">彼此鼓勵</span></span>都好緊要嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/12.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8667af05f32e2725b5504b19f8092f5488316e5d","tid":1425983,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:11:14.000Z","msg":"冇人有經歷?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af7fb0cf0094d8d5d632710159e197454a7cf184","tid":1425983,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:12:27.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2060c1271b46be93d743a7a8b7ed79e1abb7977","tid":1425983,"uid":147696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:13:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一齊和你飛</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"806f5bfa54205f1c107dcf36824816d034f3799c","tid":1425983,"uid":134563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:13:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ab